<div class="w3-content w3-container w3-padding-64">
  <h2>Serie A results</h2>
  <p class="w3-padding-16">This is a collection of interactive (well, just a little bit) heatmaps showing all results of each club that played in Serie A from the 1986-87 season to the 2016-17 season. Put your cursor on a square to see the result of any specific game.<br>
  <b>Step 1 - Data collection</b><br>
  I used <a href="https://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/">Beautifulsoup</a> to extract data from the website of the <a href="http://www.legaseriea.it/en/serie-a-tim/archive">Lega Serie A</a> and saved the data into a csv.<br>
  <b>Step 2 - Data manipulation</b><br>
  I then organised the data into Pandas DataFrames and created a dictionary with a DataFrame for each club.<br>
  <b>Step 3 - Data visualisation</b><br>
  Finally I used <a href="https://bokeh.pydata.org/en/latest/">Bokeh</a> to create the heatmaps and add the tooltip on hovering.<br><br></p>
  <h4>Please be patient, it may take about 30 seconds to load</h4>
</div>

    
